{"tid":1970467,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】央視吹捧習近平戰『疫』兵法 ── 知己知彼 百戰不殆","createTime":"2020-04-13T07:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T23:37:06.000Z","uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"013cfff15fde4db27be6ce7ca4df0383b6a08fd6","tid":1970467,"uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T07:28:54.000Z","msg":"古有孫子兵法，今有習總戰疫大法。2月底，武漢肺炎全國蔓延之際，中宣部高調宣佈將出版《大國戰「疫」》，但最終未出版先下架。踏入4月，疫情正虐肆全球，央視重磅推出題為〈習近平戰『疫』兵法──知己知彼 百戰不殆〉的文章，將習吹捧為「領導武漢肺炎戰疫的『總指揮』」，不僅稱抗疫獲得「全面勝利」，更把習與中國古代兵家看齊。有網民留言寫道：「（要教識）學生群體如何識別邪教騙術。」<br />\n<br />\n國家宣傳機器正傾全力吹捧「習兵法」，「『兵者，國之大事，死生之地，存亡之道，不可不察也。』新冠肺炎疫情發生後，習近平總書記高度重視，把疫情防控作為頭等大事來抓，始終親自指揮、親自部署。從『遭遇戰』到『阻擊戰』，從『重中之重』到『人民戰爭』，從『頭等大事』到『全面勝利』&hellip;&hellip;觀勢、謀局、落子，總書記在親自指揮這場人民戰爭的過程中，很多對策、措施與中國古代兵家思想高度契合」。央視表示，因此推出「人民領袖」欄目推出系列特稿《習近平戰「疫」兵法》，與大家一同領悟其中精髓。<br />\n<br />\n央視將《孫子&middot;謀攻篇》中「知己知彼，百戰不殆」應用在習總身上，吹捧習「指揮專家團隊確立臨床救治和藥物、疫苗研發、檢測技術和產品、病毒病原學和流行病學、動物模型構建等，動員全國科技力量防控疫情」。<br />\n<br />\n《孫子&middot;九地篇》提到的「短兵相接，分秒必爭」，讚習總自疫情爆發逾1個月後、即2月3日召開治局常務委員會作出要求，3月2日就到北京考察防控科研，詢問藥物臨床應用、生?供應保障情況，並強調「挽救更多患者生命是當務之急、重中之重」。<br />\n<br />\n央視又引用唐朝吳兢《貞觀政要&middot;納諫》「備豫不虞，為國常道」，提到習總曾表示：「人類同疾病較量最有力的武器就是科學技術，人類戰勝大災大疫離不開科學發展和技術創新。」又把科研比作「強大的戰鬥力」，強調會「贏得這場人民戰爭的最終勝利」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200412/HOLJYXBBQI27SFP4YJJVMCUTBM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200412%2FHOLJYXBBQI27SFP4YJJVMCUTBM%2F&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWSpZd1NrJsyKidS%2BVLva3MM%3D&h=7c940c93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200412%2FHOLJYXBBQI27SFP4YJJVMCUTBM%2F&h=eb87ebc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200412/HOLJYXBBQI27SFP4YJJVMCUTBM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae10754778e3942ce6720ba718f49dd98a705759","tid":1970467,"uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200412/large/1586660478_99a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200412%2Flarge%2F1586660478_99a4.jpg&h=6de8c4c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6c9082b8ab32e81f044e508543e8c31c651156f","tid":1970467,"uid":65429,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T07:31:09.000Z","msg":"中二病發😑"},{"pid":"e5c5d21785bb4c6b25f409196de99589d4ad9535","tid":1970467,"uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T07:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://p2.img.cctvpic.com/photoworkspace/contentimg/2020/04/12/2020041200495172733.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.img.cctvpic.com%2Fphotoworkspace%2Fcontentimg%2F2020%2F04%2F12%2F2020041200495172733.jpg&h=0d6a43bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p5.img.cctvpic.com/photoworkspace/contentimg/2020/04/12/2020041200133777771.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp5.img.cctvpic.com%2Fphotoworkspace%2Fcontentimg%2F2020%2F04%2F12%2F2020041200133777771.jpg&h=fcb1c3fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.img.cctvpic.com/photoworkspace/contentimg/2020/04/12/2020041200584492249.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.img.cctvpic.com%2Fphotoworkspace%2Fcontentimg%2F2020%2F04%2F12%2F2020041200584492249.jpg&h=606032fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p4.img.cctvpic.com/photoworkspace/contentim